Package mansionBandit.network

Interface Summary
Message The Message interface represents serializable network messages intended for communication between a Client and Server about game status.
 

Class Summary
Client A client receives information about the current game world and uses it to update its local copy.
ClientDisconnectMessage A ClientDisconnectMessage is to be sent to the Server containing the username of the Client that is disconnecting from the Server.
ItemUpdateMessage Represents the main form of serializable data transfer over the I/O streams for Mansion Bandit game status.
Server The Server receives updates from clients via a socket.
StringMessage Represents a network sendable String.
